    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1864-11-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1864-11-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="374"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d374">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Campbell</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 8]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                                >Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1864-11-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 19, 1864</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> It is understood here, with sincere regret, that
                    Baron Wetterstedt has been ordered to Mexico on a mission of some character
                    before coming to this country as the diplomatic agent of Sweden. It is proper
                    that you should without delay inform the minister of foreign affairs that the
                    proceeding referred to is, for obvious reasons, far from satisfactory to this
                    government, and that if it should not prevent the Baron’s official reception
                    here, it would certainly make him less welcome.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">James H. Campbell</hi>, Esq., &amp;<hi rend="italic"
                            >c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic"
                            >c</hi>.<hi rend="italic">, Stockholm.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
